{"meta": {"centerNodeId": "taxonomy-species-pluvialis-dominica", "centerNodeType": "taxonomy", "generatedAt": "2026-05-28T16:28:22", "includedNodeCount": 3, "includedLinkCount": 2, "layoutMode": "precomputed-static"}, "center": {"id": "taxonomy-species-pluvialis-dominica", "name": "美洲金斑鸻", "type": "taxonomy"}, "nodes": [{"id": "bird-美洲金鸻-dd6926cd", "name": "美洲金鸻", "englishName": "American golden plover", "latinName": "Pluvialis dominica", "type": "bird", "status": "LC", "summary": "美洲金鸻（台湾作美洲金斑鴴）（学名：Pluvialis dominica），为鸻科斑鸻属的鸟类。该物种的模式产地在伊斯帕尼奥拉岛。 美洲金鸻体重约151.47克，翼长约181.8毫米，嘴峰长约26.3毫米，喙宽度约3.8毫米，喙厚度约5.1毫米，跗蹠长约39.9毫米，尾长约65.8毫米。美洲金鸻是候鸟，其栖息在开放的草原环境中，食性为肉食性，主要食物来源是陆生无脊椎动物。 美洲金鸻在阿拉斯加和加拿大北部繁殖；越冬于南美洲南部，主要在阿根廷东部和邻近的巴拉圭和巴西南部。 参考文献 美洲金斑鸻 Pluvialis dominica Müller, 1776. 台湾物种名录. 台湾: 中央研究院生物多样性研究中心. [2013-01-24] （中文（台湾））.", "shortSummary": "美洲金鸻（台湾作美洲金斑鴴）（学名：Pluvialis dominica），为鸻科斑鸻属的鸟类。该物种的模式产地在伊斯帕尼奥拉岛。 美洲金鸻体重约151.47克，翼长约181.8毫米，嘴峰长约26.3毫米，喙宽度约3.8毫米，喙厚度约5.1毫米，跗蹠长约39.9毫米，尾长约65…", "locations": ["南美洲"], "imageUrl": "https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/0/0c/American_Golden_Plover_%287458262530%29.jpg/960px-American_Golden_Plover_%287458262530%29.jpg", "order": "Charadriiformes", "family": "Charadriidae", "genus": "Pluvialis", "species": "Pluvialis dominica", "orderCn": "鸻形目", "familyCn": "鸻科", "genusCn": "斑鸻属", "speciesCn": "美洲金斑鸻", "kingdomId": "taxonomy-kingdom-animalia", "phylumId": "taxonomy-phylum-chordata", "classId": "taxonomy-class-aves", "orderId": "taxonomy-order-charadriiformes", "familyId": "taxonomy-family-charadriidae", "genusId": "taxonomy-genus-pluvialis", "speciesId": "taxonomy-species-pluvialis-dominica", "taxonomyIds": {"kingdom": "taxonomy-kingdom-animalia", "phylum": "taxonomy-phylum-chordata", "class": "taxonomy-class-aves", "order": "taxonomy-order-charadriiformes", "family": "taxonomy-family-charadriidae", "genus": "taxonomy-genus-pluvialis", "species": "taxonomy-species-pluvialis-dominica"}, "expandable": true, "x": -1000.62, "y": 152.18, "z